{"word":"Swine","slug":"swine","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Swine</b> Forbidden as food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=7'>Lev 11:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=14&verse=8'>Deu 14:8</a><br/> Used for food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=65&verse=4'>Isa 65:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=66&verse=17'>Isa 66:17</a><br/> Used for sacrifice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=66&verse=3'>Isa 66:3</a><br/> Wild boar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=80&verse=13'>Psa 80:13</a><br/> Jewels in the nose of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=11&verse=22'>Pro 11:22</a><br/> Viciousness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=7&verse=6'>Mat 7:6</a><br/> Jesus sends devils into<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=32'>Mat 8:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=5&verse=14'>Mar 5:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=33'>Luk 8:33</a><br/> Feeding of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=15&verse=16'>Luk 15:16</a><br/> Sow returns to her wallow<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=2&verse=22'>2Pe 2:22</a>"}]}